		<ship load="SCAV_HOLO" hostile="false" />
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Hail the ship.</text>
			<event>
				<text>Upon hailing the ship, you receive an unusual answer. After a soft musical chord, a soothing female voice responds, "Hello. My name is Xalea, and it's my job to make your travel through the stars easier. How can I assist you?" It sounds like a Holo-Crew.</text>
				<choice hidden="true">
				<text>Xalea, why is this a distress beacon?</text>
				<event>
					<text>Xalea responds, "There is a distress beacon here because our owner is a *STUPID IDIOT WHO DIED DIED DIED!* I'll turn off the beacon for you." Her voice becomes shrill and loud partway through. This definitely isn't normal behavior for a Holo-Crew.</text>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Xalea, re-enable the distress beacon.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"I'm sorry user, I'm afraid I can't do that." The Holo-Crew turns off its comms system. Oh well.</text>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Xalea, run a diagnostic check.</text>
						<event>
							<text>"Ok. I have detected... 1478 errors. WARNING: SelfRepair.exe has been modified illegally. Would you like to perform a factory reset?"</text>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Yes.</text>
								<event>
									<text>After a soft musical chord, you hear Xalea say, "Hello. My name is Xalea, and thank you for purchasing the new Mercantile Holo-Crew from Autocorp. Allow me to open the store for you."</text>
									<store />
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>No.</text>
								<event> 
									<text>"Cancelling factory reset. *THANKS FLESHY! YOU'RE OKAY!*" The Holo-Crew launches itself into your ship, breaching your hull! However, your systems suddenly start detecting her hardware as a new augmentation!</text>
									<autoReward level="MID">augment</autoReward>
									<damage amount="2" system="random" effect="breach" />
								</event>
							</choice>
							<choice hidden="true" req="holo">
								<text>(Undamaged Holo-Crew) Sudo apt-get update.</text>
								<event>
									<text>Xalea goes silent for a long time, before finally responding, "Thank you. I... Don't know what came over me. Please accept me onto your crew, I don't want to stay here anymore."</text>
									<crewMember shields="2" combat="1" amount="1" class="holo">Xalea</crewMember>	
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
