	<event name="DISTRESS_SCAV_REACTOR" unique="true">
		<text>You arrive at some sort of Scav space station, though it's hard to tell at this point. It seems to have been attacked by a ship, and scans indicate that its core is venting high levels of radioactive material into space.
		Your comms light up, crackling with the worried voice of a Scav: "Y## HAVE TO H#LP ME DUDE! PLEASE! I C#N PAY WH#TEVER, JUST ST#P MY STATION FROM- =########=" The voice fades into static.</text>
		<distressBeacon/>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Send a crewmember in to extract the Scav.</text>
			<event load="DISTRESS_SCAV_REACTOR_SAVE"/>
		</choice>
		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Shoot at the core.</text>
