		</choice>
		<choice hidden="true" req="teleporter" lvl="2">
			<text>(Advanced Teleporter) Attempt to teleport the Scav.</text>
			<event>
				<text>The Scav appears in your teleporter room and reluctantly thanks you. "I gu#ss this is the b#st that could be- =########= I may n#t have any more st#ff to give, but I can p#y my dues by work#ng on your ship at least."</text>
				<crewMember engines="1" amount="1" class="scav" />
			</event>
