		<choice hidden="true">
			<text>Leave the Scav to his fate.</text>
			<event>
				<text>You prepare to jump away. Your comms crackle with the Scav's desperate cries for help, but there's nothing you could've done to save him. At least, that's what you tell yourself.</text>
